{"tid":1631834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"左膠可唔可以唔好當前線係弱智","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:56.000Z","uid":58841,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"863fb71f22fd6c84302e9e0be837ebdc4464050b","tid":1631834,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"你地自己弱智就算啦<br />\n唔好諗到其他人同你地係同一個級別好無呀<br />\n睇撚死你地未落過場望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班前線謹慎到呢<br />\n一見有狗就即走<br />\n做野之前又要諗其他人點諗<br />\n又要驚自己累街坊<br />\n講真係唔洗負責任<br />\n叫你班左膠做街坊擋下都呀吱呀咗<br />\n所謂既哨原來係透過直播/係屋企望出去就叫哨<br />\n你老母我落去做哨做街坊 前面隻green object同我距離一米都無都未撚驚過<br />\n連咁簡單既野都唔肯做其實憑乜野亂咁指指點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7246b867314ab717bcea28b4edaecb54148ded0d","tid":1631834,"uid":227441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"至左膠廢老: 你老母聽日會俾人屌10次再殺撚埋佢, 跟住你老豆再屌你老母條屍, 屌完再活生生燒死你老豆, 再吊你全家上IFC示眾俾全世界知你冚家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e67b217420316167b0f5acfe6bb6dfdfcbc79b","tid":1631834,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"我想講你街坊LOOK唔出聲隻狗係唔會理你<br />\n隻狗無蒙面仲會扮哂好人<br />\n你想嗌又淆底咪企後少少囉"},{"pid":"5ac73b81045a236dd5622b6543c53d5dae686f52","tid":1631834,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"狗隻最低警覺性就係廿幾歲同上左年紀既街坊<br />\n偏偏你地就最撚無膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7d12b22093f9e9879a7705c8dfc1fec744529e","tid":1631834,"uid":114090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:02.000Z","msg":"白卡佬你真係好撚正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係你fans"},{"pid":"eb06d9c513f712e1069b87910555db5f53c071d5","tid":1631834,"uid":177736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰</span>"},{"pid":"eb05f4a06820b10f7456156daf15404b6a5ff03d","tid":1631834,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"c388581f0d6987f493bf8b9e3b64dd263b02a3c2","tid":1631834,"uid":153186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"剛柔並重 先降半級 黑色只限港共建築物+黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f7ed6906d75d3f4ba2da57cb4d019a5a2bd1eb","tid":1631834,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[18區開花] 一句講晒，聽日一點定八點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"}]}